      "text": "Account Number: \nReservation Number: MMDDVENUE_CODEAM/PM\nVENUE: \nPlease set up on DAY, MONTH DAY_NO, at TIME AM/PM\nSETUP_INSTRUCTION (Already present)\nPlease break down Day in the AM or\nPlease breakdown in the PM or AM (depending on the next event)\nor Please breakdown on DAY, MONTH DAY_NO, at TIME AM/PM",
